content.rendered:
Prestige Motorcars is privileged to be part of the PCI’s Cipali-Cirebon Touring event and honored to meet the children of Yayasan Insan Kamil Kalimasada and Sultan Kacirebonan IX Pangeran Raja Abdulgani Nata Diningrat Dekarangga.

To the Sultan and all of the staff at the Yayasan Insan Kamil, you are doing God’s work. And for that, we thank you
